![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/4a02902d-0487-4965-b45b-dd0fe806b6de/20240722_170636.jpg?format=original)

GUNTHER opens RAW with a promo calling everyone in Judgement Day “Street Trash" and proclaiming the formerly homeless Damien Priest a “BUM"

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/4a3ec018-eb59-40f7-88d0-b80c8096a726/20240722_170959.jpg?format=original)

No words needed for Priest as he comes out and gets right into a brawl with GUNTHER. Incredibly awkward commercial break takes us from the action as it's broken up.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/3377880f-e0dd-48b6-a0ef-f68b0675d749/20240722_171409.jpg?format=original)

Back from break and they're still crawling backstage.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/c956f429-26b4-4248-b1eb-7fc610e418e2/20240722_171838.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_BRON BREAKER DEF. ILJA DRAGUNOV_**
    

Incredible opening match. Very stiff. Ilja and Breakker are on even ground the entire match until Breakker slaughters Dragunov with a mid air spear while Dragunov dove off the apron.

Dragunov is declared unable to continue and BRON wins the match.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/4abe8adf-7e55-4454-b86b-5831200fcf21/20240722_173730.jpg?format=original)

The Judgement Day are backstage beating up Jey Uso in the WWE 2K video game. Rhea walks up and Dom asks her what's up with Jey Uso? Rhea says it's nothing.

Dom wants to fight Jey Uso but Rhea says no. Finn asks why is she protecting Jey? Rhea says she doesn't want to go to war with Jey and leaves.

Carlito, Finn Balor and JD tell Dom he knows what he has to do to Jey Uso.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/4f599334-36bf-49c1-8ab2-394c26041873/20240722_180732.jpg?format=original)

Jelly Roll will be performing live at SummerSlam next Saturday.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/9ac6dfc8-2d88-44a1-8f15-6fdf366d09e1/20240722_180838.jpg?format=original)

SONYA DEVILLE DEF. LYRA VALKYRIA

Decent match that ends when Lyra is distracted and Sonya hits her with her finisher

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/2d576343-f02f-4614-a42b-9189a461e736/Screenshot_20240722_180240.jpg?format=original)

CM Punk announced he is officially clear to return to action. He calls out Drew McIntyre to fight. McIntyre says Punk vs Drew is much bigger than Wisconsin.

Adam Pearce says the match is official and Seth Rollins will be the guest Ref at Summerslam.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/db8a2ba1-8ab1-476b-b9d1-217bd893bf63/Screenshot_20240722_182738.jpg?format=original)

Sami Zayn is doing an interview when he overheard Jey Uso being jumped by Carlito and JD McDonough. Sami runs over and saves Jey

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/d04d2f91-2e42-46de-a516-9970fdd4e9cb/Screenshot_20240722_182800.jpg?format=original)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/e222f3ea-61b4-4299-8b92-a9fd8b529ba1/20240722_182820.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_FINAL TESTAMENT DEF. XAVIER WOODS, OTIS AND AKIRA TOZAWA_**
    

After the match, Chad Gable and the Creed Bros confront Otis, Maxxine and TOZAWA.

Gable gives Otis, Maxxine and TOZAWA one last chance to come back to Alpha Academy.

They decline. So the Creed Brothers attack them. Otis fights them off and attacks Gable but the Creed Bros save Gable and take down Otis 3 on 1.

Until the Wyatt 6 arrive!!!!!!! UNCLE HOWDY ATTACKS GABLE!!!

SISTER ABIGAIL TO A MASSIVE POP!!!!

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/f9b2cca3-334c-4410-96ee-73435d9d0642/20240722_183352.jpg?format=original)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1d1fd547-e794-4718-9cb4-fd49dd68a11e/20240722_185735.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_PETE DUNNE VS BRONSON REED ENDS IN A NO CONTEST_**
    

Sheamus runs out and attacks them both

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/45b2f4d8-9742-4706-97f1-b833f5386f0d/Screenshot_20240722_185207.jpg?format=original)

Rhea Ripley is furious that Jey Uso was jumped and now Sami Zayn is involved. She wants to know where Dom and Finn were when Jey got jumped...

Carlito says... you should ask Liv.

Rhea drags Dom out to the ring.

NOT COOL 😂😂

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/81a10409-ae4a-4daa-a35e-7769cd2c1da0/PhotoGrid_1_20240722190143.jpg?format=original)

**_"Gorgeous men like Dominik go for girls that look like me"_**

**_Liv Morgan to Rhea Ripley_**

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/58a43b74-63bc-4b34-8947-e8419ddb462b/PhotoGrid_1_20240722190451.jpg?format=original)

Rhea Ripley drags Dominik out to the ring and says Liv can come get him if she wants him. Liv stays in the crowd area and confessed her love for Dom.

Dom says he hates her and curses her out in Spanish. She leaves crying and Rhea Ripley is finally happy with her Papi.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/837fd74a-4337-4075-aa4a-f0865670f2a1/20240722_192754.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **ZELINA VEGA DEF. ZOEY STARKS**
    

This is Zelina's first victory on the main roster since August of 2023

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/437f0bec-b454-4c5e-a1bd-c1466b9cce73/20240722_200356.jpg?format=original)

SAMI ZAYN AND JEY USO DEF. JUDGEMENT DAY

Pinning the tag thanks should earn them a shot at the title? No time to figure that out as Bron Breakker attacks Sami Zayn to close the show.

